data.description: Explore the perfect mix of suburban peace and city access in this 4-bedroom home, ideal for families seeking both space and comfort. Located in the friendly Travis Ranch community near Lake Ray Hubbard, and just minutes from Downtown Dallas, this property combines a quiet setting with proximity to city life. The home features a versatile layout including an extra room perfect as a fifth bedroom, nursery, or office. An open foyer leads to a spacious great room and an adjoining café area, great for family gatherings. The heart of the home is a large kitchen with a central island, ideal for entertaining and everyday living. This open-concept area extends to a dining space and great room. Upstairs, a sizable loft offers additional recreational space. Privacy and comfort are assured with an owner’s suite and bedrooms across both levels. Choose this inviting home for a superb balance of lifestyle and convenience, crafted with your family’s needs in mind!
